languages.text: "...но мне нужно думать о будущем. Мы остались без гроша, и я не хочу, чтобы мои дочери оставались в этом ужасном месте ни минутой дольше необходимого".

traits.locale_text: "...но мне нужно думать о будущем. Мы остались без гроша, и я не хочу, чтобы мои дочери оставались в этом ужасном месте ни минутой дольше необходимого".

languages.text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

languages.text: 「でも未来のことを考えなくてはな。助けられる手だてもないし、娘たちにはこんな恐ろしいところに一分たりとも長くいてほしくない」
languages.original_text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

traits.locale_text: 「でも未来のことを考えなくてはな。助けられる手だてもないし、娘たちにはこんな恐ろしいところに一分たりとも長くいてほしくない」

languages.text: « Cela dit, il faut bien que je pense à l'avenir. Nous n'avons plus aucun moyen de subvenir à nos besoins, et je ne tiens pas à ce que mes filles passent une minute de plus que nécessaire dans cet endroit abject. »
languages.original_text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

traits.locale_text: « Cela dit, il faut bien que je pense à l'avenir. Nous n'avons plus aucun moyen de subvenir à nos besoins, et je ne tiens pas à ce que mes filles passent une minute de plus que nécessaire dans cet endroit abject. »

languages.text: “不过，我必须得为未来做好打算。我们已经失去了生活的来源，而且这个地方这么可怕，我甚至不愿意让我的女儿们在这里多待一分钟。”
languages.original_text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

traits.locale_text: “不过，我必须得为未来做好打算。我们已经失去了生活的来源，而且这个地方这么可怕，我甚至不愿意让我的女儿们在这里多待一分钟。”

languages.text: "Dennoch muss ich an die Zukunft denken. Uns wurde keine Unterstützung zuteil, und meine Töchter sollen nicht länger an diesem schrecklichen Ort bleiben als unbedingt nötig."
languages.original_text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

traits.locale_text: "Dennoch muss ich an die Zukunft denken. Uns wurde keine Unterstützung zuteil, und meine Töchter sollen nicht länger an diesem schrecklichen Ort bleiben als unbedingt nötig."

languages.text: «Debería pensar en nuestro futuro. Nos hemos quedado sin nada para subsistir, y no querría que mis hijas pasasen ni un minuto más en este espantoso lugar».
languages.original_text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

traits.locale_text: «Debería pensar en nuestro futuro. Nos hemos quedado sin nada para subsistir, y no querría que mis hijas pasasen ni un minuto más en este espantoso lugar».

languages.text: "Yine de geleceği düşünmek zorundayım. Geçim kaynağımız yok. Kızlarımın zorunda kalmadıkça bu dehşet verici yerde bir dakika daha durmalarını istemiyorum."
languages.original_text: "Yet I must think about the future. We have been left without means of support, and I do not wish for my daughters to stay in this dreadful place a minute longer than they have to."

traits.locale_text: "Yine de geleceği düşünmek zorundayım. Arkamızda herhangi bir destek kalmadı ve kızlarımın zorunda kalmadıkça bu dehşet verici yerde bir dakika daha durmalarını istemiyorum."
